msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by wrong thought are bad results. "

msgctxt "an10.114:4.4"
msgid "sammāsaṅkappapaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, ayaṃ attho. (2) "
msgstr "And the many skillful qualities fully developed because of right thought are good results. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
